---
import Layout from "../../components/Layout.astro";
import { FloatingOrbs } from "../../components/FloatingOrbs";
import { ScrollReveal } from "../../components/ScrollReveal";
import { InstallCommand } from "../../components/InstallCommand";
import { BookOpen, ArrowRight, Terminal, Heart, Sparkles, Globe, Shield, Code, Clock } from "lucide-react";
import { getT } from "../../i18n.server";

export const getStaticPaths = () => [{ params: { lang: "es" } }, { params: { lang: "en" } }, { params: { lang: "it" } }];

const lng = (Astro.currentLocale ?? "es") as "es" | "en" | "it";
const t = getT(lng);

const title = `${t.docs.title} — Lydia Agent`;

const sections = [
  { title: t.docs.quickstart, href: "#quickstart" },
  { title: t.docs.install, href: "#install" },
  { title: t.docs.provider, href: "#provider" },
  { title: t.docs.gateway, href: "#gateway" },
  { title: t.docs.cli, href: "#cli" },
  { title: t.docs.cron, href: "#cron" },
  { title: t.docs.skills, href: "#skills" },
];
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-rpm-highlight-low/60 bg-rpm-base py-28">
    <FloatingOrbs client:load />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 mask-radial-fade bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--color-rpm-foam)_0%,_transparent_50%)] opacity-20" aria-hidden></div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
      <ScrollReveal client:visible>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-rpm-foam/30 bg-rpm-foam/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-rpm-foam">
          <BookOpen className="h-3.5 w-3.5" />
          {t.docs.badge}
        </div>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={0.1}>
        <h1 class="mt-6 font-display text-5xl leading-tight text-rpm-text sm:text-6xl text-balance">{t.docs.title}</h1>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={0.2}>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-rpm-subtle">{t.docs.subtitle}</p>
      </ScrollReveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-rpm-surface/20 py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-3">
            <h3 class="font-display text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-rpm-muted">{t.docs.onThisPage}</h3>
            <nav class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              {sections.map((s) => (
                <a href={s.href} class="text-sm text-rpm-subtle transition hover:text-rpm-iris">{s.title}</a>
              ))}
            </nav>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-16">
          <ScrollReveal client:visible>
            <div id="quickstart" class="rounded-2xl border border-rpm-highlight-med/40 bg-rpm-base/60 p-8">
              <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl text-rpm-text">{t.docs.quickstart}</h2>
              <p class="mb-6 text-rpm-subtle">Lydia Agent es una CLI multiplataforma escrita en Python. Tras la instalación puedes empezar a lanzar tareas, gestionar skills y conectar gateways.</p>
              <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-rpm-surface/80 p-4 text-center">
                  <div class="mb-2 flex justify-center text-rpm-iris"><Terminal className="h-6 w-6" /></div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-medium text-rpm-text">1. Instala</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-rpm-surface/80 p-4 text-center">
                  <div class="mb-2 flex justify-center text-rpm-foam"><Globe className="h-6 w-6" /></div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-medium text-rpm-text">2. Configura</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-rpm-surface/80 p-4 text-center">
                  <div class="mb-2 flex justify-center text-rpm-love"><Sparkles className="h-6 w-6" /></div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-medium text-rpm-text">3. Ejecuta</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </ScrollReveal>

          <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={0.1}>
            <div id="install" class="rounded-2xl border border-rpm-highlight-med/40 bg-rpm-base/60 p-8">
              <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl text-rpm-text">{t.docs.install}</h2>
              <p class="mb-6 text-rpm-subtle">Copia el comando según tu sistema operativo y ejecútalo en la terminal.</p>
              <InstallCommand client:visible />
            </div>
          </ScrollReveal>

          <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={0.15}>
            <div id="provider" class="rounded-2xl border border-rpm-highlight-med/40 bg-rpm-base/60 p-8">
              <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl text-rpm-text">{t.docs.provider}</h2>
              <p class="mb-4 text-rpm-subtle">Lydia soporta múltiples proveedores a través de OpenRouter, Anthropic, OpenAI y compatibles. Define tu preferencia por CLI:</p>
              <pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl bg-rpm-surface/90 p-5 text-sm text-rpm-text"><code>{`lydia config set model.provider openrouter
lydia config set model.model anthropic/claude-sonnet-4
lydia config set model.api_key $OPENROUTER_API_KEY`}</code></pre>
            </div>
          </ScrollReveal>

          <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={0.2}>
            <div id="gateway" class="rounded-2xl border border-rpm-highlight-med/40 bg-rpm-base/60 p-8">
              <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl text-rpm-text">{t.docs.gateway}</h2>
              <p class="mb-4 text-rpm-subtle">Habilita gateways para recibir mensajes o enviar notificaciones. Telegram y Discord funcionan sin servidores adicionales.</p>
              <div class="space-y-3 font-mono text-sm text-rpm-subtle">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg bg-rpm-surface/80 p-4 border-l-4 border-rpm-iris"><Globe className="h-4 w-4 text-rpm-iris" /><code>lydia config set gateways.telegram true</code></div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg bg-rpm-surface/80 p-4 border-l-4 border-rpm-foam"><Code className="h-4 w-4 text-rpm-foam" /><code>lydia config set gateways.discord true</code></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </ScrollReveal>

          <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={0.25}>
            <div id="cli" class="rounded-2xl border border-rpm-highlight-med/40 bg-rpm-base/60 p-8">
              <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl text-rpm-text">{t.docs.cli}</h2>
              <div class="space-y-4 font-mono text-sm text-rpm-subtle">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg bg-rpm-surface/80 p-4 border-l-4 border-rpm-iris"><Terminal className="h-4 w-4 text-rpm-iris" /><code>lydia config set model.provider openrouter</code></div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg bg-rpm-surface/80 p-4 border-l-4 border-rpm-rose"><Heart className="h-4 w-4 text-rpm-rose" /><code>lydia skills install github-code-review</code></div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg bg-rpm-surface/80 p-4 border-l-4 border-rpm-foam"><Sparkles className="h-4 w-4 text-rpm-foam" /><code>lydia cronjob create --name "daily-brief" --schedule "0 9 * * *"</code></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </ScrollReveal>

          <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={0.3}>
            <div id="cron" class="rounded-2xl border border-rpm-highlight-med/40 bg-rpm-base/60 p-8">
              <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl text-rpm-text">{t.docs.cron}</h2>
              <p class="mb-4 text-rpm-subtle">Programa trabajos recurrentes que ejecuten un prompt, un script o una skill de forma autónoma.</p>
              <pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl bg-rpm-surface/90 p-5 text-sm text-rpm-text"><code>{`lydia cronjob create --name morning-brief \
  --schedule "0 8 * * *" \
  --prompt "Resumen de PRs y tareas pendientes" \
  --deliver telegram`}</code></pre>
            </div>
          </ScrollReveal>

          <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={0.35}>
            <div id="skills" class="rounded-2xl border border-rpm-highlight-med/40 bg-rpm-base/60 p-8">
              <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl text-rpm-text">{t.docs.skills}</h2>
              <p class="mb-6 text-rpm-subtle">Las skills son memoria procedural reutilizable. Puedes instalarlas del registro o crear las tuyas en <code class="rounded bg-rpm-surface px-1 py-0.5 font-mono text-rpm-iris">~/.lydia/skills/</code>.</p>
              <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-rpm-surface/80 p-4"><div class="mb-2 text-rpm-iris"><Shield className="h-5 w-5" /></div><p class="text-sm font-medium text-rpm-text">Seguridad por defecto</p></div>
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-rpm-surface/80 p-4"><div class="mb-2 text-rpm-foam"><Clock className="h-5 w-5" /></div><p class="text-sm font-medium text-rpm-text">Automatización recurrente</p></div>
              </div>
              <a href={`/${lng}/features`} class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-rpm-iris px-5 py-2.5 font-medium text-rpm-base transition hover:bg-rpm-foam">
                {t.featurePreview.ctaFeatures} <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4" />
              </a>
            </div>
          </ScrollReveal>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
